Name: [Shock] Mosquito Swatter
Desc: Each stack of Zap increases the Agent's <color=#2EB6FF>Electric Anomaly Buildup Rate</color> by <color=#2BAD00>3%</color>.
Desc2: With this powerful and convenient tool, you won't need to tap with your hands anymore. The only downside is that it may emit the smell of burnt meat if you use it for too long...
